snippet.title: Blabyrinth Trailer
snippet.description:
Blabyrinth is a multiplayer escape room for mobile devices that changes every time you play! From the creator of Spaceteam. Coming soon for iOS and Android.
Visit http://blabyrinth.com for more info.
